===Etymology===
Latin ''[[ad]] + [[illiam]] + [[horam]]''

===Pronunciation===
allóra, /alˈlora/, /<tt>al"lora</tt>/
===Adverb===
'''allora'''

# [[so]], [[well then]]
#:'''Allora''', che cosa c'è di nuovo? - So, what's new?
# at that time
#:La bambina era '''allora''' chiamata da tutti gattina per la sua dolcezza. - At that time, the child was called "kittie" by everybody because of her sweetness.''

